US sues BP over Gulf of Mexico oil disaster <TIMEX3 tid="t3" type="DATE" value="2010-12-16">16 December 2010</TIMEX3> Last updated at 06:54 GMT Help The United States is to sue BP and eight other companies over a huge oil spill in the Gulf of Mexico .
The government said it would hold the firms fully accountable for the billions of dollars spent on cleaning up the worst environmental disaster in US history .
Eleven men died in the explosion on the Deepwater Horizon drilling rig in <TIMEX3 tid="t6" type="DATE" value="2010-04">April</TIMEX3> .
The BBC 's Iain MacKenzie reports .
